# Keep the build context small and deterministic.
**/.git
**/.gitignore
**/.gitattributes
**/.github

# .NET build outputs
**/bin
**/obj
**/out
**/publish
**/TestResults
**/*.user
**/*.suo
**/.vs
**/.vscode
**/.idea

# Node / Angular (W2 sonrasi `web/` icin)
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/.angular

# Secrets / env / IDE clutter
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example
**/appsettings.*.local.json
**/*.local.json

# Docs / large assets that shouldn't be inside images
docs/
*.md
LICENSE

# Test projects shouldn't end up in the API image build context unnecessarily,
# but `dotnet restore -p:SolutionDir=...` would walk slnx and pull them in. We
# avoid that by restoring with the csproj path directly (see Dockerfile).
tests/

# OS
**/.DS_Store
**/Thumbs.db
